Kardan Israel Ltd. (KRIS)  is in talks to
sell half of its 68.3 percent stake in Dan Vehicle &
Transportation Ltd., Calcalist reported, without saying where it
got the information.  The estimated value of the deal is 160 million shekels to
200 million shekels, Calcalist said.  A spokeswoman for Kardan Israel told Bloomberg the company
has had initial contacts regarding a sale and that itâ€™s too
